Subject: Accelerate Integration with Proven APIs - 20min Call?

Body: Hi Alex,

I noticed Acme FinTech is looking to streamline integrations. Our robust APIs can significantly reduce integration time by ~60%, as demonstrated by a similar FinTechCo that cut onboarding from 6 weeks to 2 with our APIs. This typically results in a 3-5x ROI within the first year.

Would you be available for a 20-minute discovery call to discuss how we could help Acme FinTech?

Best,
[Your Name]

- feature:api
- problem:integration
- case:fintechco
- metric:roi
